I believe Compassion comes when you make the connection to the situation & your own life..
When u go through pain, you don't want to see others go through it..
I believe throughout the whole world we are all shifting in consciousness towards making the connection with Animals, & of course so much more is to come..
I strongly feel that one of the major steps in changing the bigger picture is introducing compassion towards animals by not having them serve us as our underlings. In however way we've been taught: as food, entertainment, clothing, etc. 
They Are Earthlings Just as Much as We Are & Deserve their Undisturbed Peace on Earth as well. 
@Regrann from @earthlinglinds
